# custom.vrs  by Kent Spielmann 01/July/2014
# custom modifications to eng.vrs (English RSV versification) 
#
# This custom.vrs file compensates for differences between eng.vrs and most NIV and NIV-like translations
#
#
#---------------------------------------------------------
# Section 1: Modifications to chapter length
#---------------------------------------------------------
#
#--------------------------------------------------
# Old Testament
#--------------------------------------------------
#
# None
#
#-----------------------------------------------
# New Testament
#--------------------------------------------------
#
# NIV 2CO 13 has 14 verses like KJV. Some modern versions have 13 verses 
2CO 13:13
#  3JN has 14 verses like KJV. Some modern English versions have 15 verses 
# 3JN 1:14
# The content of REV 12:18 is included in 13:1 (like KJV - though the reading is different)
REV 12:17
#
